% =================== A. FULL-STACK SCOPE & ARCHITECTURE ===================
\item Built a full-stack doctor-appointment platform -- a \textbf{Spring Boot 3.5} (Java 17) REST API and a \textbf{React Native} (TypeScript, strict) app -- supporting separate patient and doctor experiences   % [TOP PICK]
\item Designed a layered \textbf{controller--service--repository} architecture across 10 JPA entities, 13 services, and \textasciitilde10 controllers (\textasciitilde60 REST endpoints)
\item Documented the full REST API with \textbf{OpenAPI/Swagger} (SpringDoc)
\item Modeled the domain in \textbf{PostgreSQL} with unique constraints (phone + country) and composite indexes

% =================== B. AUTHENTICATION & SECURITY ===================
\item Implemented \textbf{JWT} (HS256) authentication with \textbf{BCrypt} password hashing and \textbf{role-based authorization} (doctor/patient) on a stateless Spring Security filter chain   % [TOP PICK]
\item Built a custom \texttt{JwtAuthFilter} that validates token signature/expiry and injects role and userId claims on every request
\item Configured stateless sessions, CORS, and a token-based security model for the mobile client
\item Implemented \textbf{AES-256} encrypted upload and storage of clinical documents with role-based access control   % [verify implementation before relying on it]

% =================== C. CONCURRENCY & DATA INTEGRITY ===================
\item Prevented double-booking of doctor slots under concurrent requests using \textbf{JPA optimistic locking} (\texttt{@Version}) with automatic \textbf{retry and exponential backoff} (\texttt{@Retryable}, 3 attempts), ensuring consistency without pessimistic DB locks   % [TOP PICK]
\item Wrapped booking and state-transition logic in \texttt{@Transactional} boundaries for ACID guarantees
\item Enforced appointment state transitions and unique appointment numbers via a JPA entity listener

% =================== D. REAL-TIME NOTIFICATIONS ===================
\item Engineered \textbf{dual-channel real-time notifications} -- STOMP \textbf{WebSocket} for in-app updates and \textbf{Firebase Cloud Messaging} for background push -- fanned out to both patient and doctor on each event   % [TOP PICK]
\item Built an FCM \textbf{device-token lifecycle} (registration, refresh handling, auto-deactivation of stale tokens)
\item Implemented role-aware \textbf{deep-linking} from push notifications to the relevant appointment screen

% =================== E. DOCTOR DISCOVERY / SEARCH ===================
\item Built dynamic doctor discovery using \textbf{JPA Specifications} with multi-criteria filters (specialization, fee, experience, rating, availability) and paginated, indexed queries   % [TOP PICK]
\item Auto-computed each doctor's average rating and review count for ranking and display

% =================== F. APPOINTMENT & SLOT MANAGEMENT ===================
\item Implemented the full appointment lifecycle (\texttt{PENDING $\rightarrow$ CONFIRMED $\rightarrow$ COMPLETED/CANCELLED/NO\_SHOW}) with doctor confirm/complete/no-show actions
\item Built \textbf{bulk slot creation} and date-scoped availability queries with flexible 15--60 minute durations

% =================== G. REVIEWS & RATINGS ===================
\item Built a \textbf{ratings \& reviews} system (1--5 stars with comments) with doctor replies and auto-aggregated per-doctor averages

% =================== H. MOBILE -- STATE & DATA LAYER ===================
\item Architected the mobile data layer with \textbf{Redux Toolkit + RTK Query} (33 endpoints) using \textbf{tag-based cache invalidation} for live data coherence   % [TOP PICK]
\item Built a \textbf{401 interceptor} that auto-detects session expiry, resets the cache, and forces re-login
\item Persisted auth state with \textbf{redux-persist + encrypted storage} for secure, cross-session tokens
\item Implemented type-safe forms with \textbf{react-hook-form + Zod} validation schemas

% =================== I. MOBILE -- REAL-TIME, NAVIGATION & UX ===================
\item Built a resilient \textbf{STOMP WebSocket} client with auto-reconnect, heartbeats, and foreground re-connection
\item Built an \textbf{FCM push} handler for foreground/background/quit states with Android 13+ runtime permissions
\item Structured \textbf{role-based navigation} (React Navigation v6): conditional Auth / Patient-tab / Doctor-tab stacks with modal overlays
\item Delivered 18 screens and 10 reusable UI components with \textbf{NativeWind/Tailwind} theming and dark-mode support
\item Built doctor search with a \textbf{5-filter bottom sheet} and 400\,ms-debounced queries, plus a booking flow with slot grid and price breakdown

% =================== J. ENGINEERING QUALITY / SCALE ===================
\item Centralized error handling with custom exceptions and a unified \texttt{ApiResponse<T>} response envelope
\item Auto-managed audit timestamps (\texttt{@CreationTimestamp}/\texttt{@UpdateTimestamp}) across all entities



